  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates which substitution solutions are used in daily clincal practice in
      various teaching hospitals in a specific district (Frankfurt/Rhine-Main Metropolitan Region).
      Furthermore the indication for usage of these solutions is investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
